              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: Ticket valid 120 days from date of purchased Adult: 13 years old & above Child: below 12 years old Free of charge for children below 90cm All published prices are subject to change without prior notice No-show forfeit Ticket Visitors are prohibited from smoking, any rough behavior, running, swimming, diving or throwing rubbish into the lake. Children at the age of 12 years and below are to be accompanied by an adult of 18 years old and above. Visitors are required to get out of the lake in the event of heavy rain, thunderstorm or electric interference and obey the instructions of the lifeguards and authorities. No refund will be given for purchase of tickets in the event of continuous bad weather or thunder storm. Outside food and drinks are not allowed at the theme park/ lake. Pedal Boat Activity & Tube Ride Activity: Pedal boats and tube ride must be used in designated area only. All visitors must wear a life jacket. The pedal boat and tube ride can only fit 2 pax. Children must be able to sit in the boat seat on their own. Users are not allowed to sit on another’s lap."
